tom" button_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwp.magnium-themes.com%2Fthebuilt%2Fthebuilt-2%2Fcore-values-2%2F|title:Read%20more||" button_icon="angle-right" button_icon_position="right" button_display="newline" button_size="small" text_size="small" text_tranform="uppercase" button_align="left" css_animation="left-to-right"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1516377681672{margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-image: url(http://projects.razorbee.com/pgbconstructions/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/builder-working-black-1.jpg?id=2921) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="prt"][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1465904326225{margin-right: 0px !important;padding-top: 40px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;}"][mgt_promo_block_wp background_color="#f1f1f1" coverimage="1" block_width="100%" block_height="400px" darken="no-darken" animated="0" text_color="black" button_url="|||" hover_effect="pulse-shrink" button_size="small" button_icon_position="right" button_text_size="large" text_tranform="uppercase" button_top_margin="enable" button_show_onhover="1" css_animation="left-to-right" unique_block_id="prt" css=".vc_custom_1516456421327{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 70px !important;padding-left: 70px !important;}"]\r\n<h5 style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #999999;">SOME FACTS</span></h5>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Great experiences\r\nbuild great brands.</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">While the Constructions makes a Building, it is the Interiors that convert the Building into a Sweet Home, or a Productive Factory. Always in close contact with the Owners,<strong>PGB Constructions</strong>provide attractive Interior Designs, after thoroughly understanding the aspirations of the Owners.<strong>PGB Constructions</strong>thoroughly understands that Interiors, be it for Commercial or Residential application, should, besides providing the much needed comfort, also represent the Taste and Values of the Occupants.</p>\r\n[/mgt_promo_block_wp][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1465902691008{margin-left: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}"][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1465903423242{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-right: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}"][vc_column_inner][mgt_icon_box_wp icon_font="eye" subtitle="OUR" title="VISION" title_position="right" color="white"]To become renowned leaders in the field of <strong>Construction &amp; Interiors</strong>with quality workmanship, High performance and reliability, Service-minded attitude, Cost-effectiveness &amp; Transform excellence with our work.[/mgt_icon_box_wp][mgt_icon_box_wp icon_font="users" animateicon="1" subtitle=" TEAM " title="PROFESSIONAL TEAMWORK" title_position="right" color="white"]\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We connect expertise across services, markets, and geographies to deliver transformative outcomes. Worldwide, we design, build, finance, operate and manage projects and programs that unlock opportunities.</p>\r\n[/mgt_icon_box_wp][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1463480863149{background-color: #1c2126 !important;}"][vc_column][mgt_calltoaction_block_wp background_color="" text_color="white" title="We are The Built" button_url="url:http%3A%2F%2Fwp.magnium-themes.com%2Fthebuilt%2Fthebuilt-2%2Fget-a-quote%2F|title:Get%20a%20quote||" hover_effect="sweep-to-bottom" button_icon="check-square-o" text_tranform="uppercase" side_paddings="0"]We help customers built World Class Construction Projects[/mgt_calltoaction_block_wp][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][mgt_header_block_wp title="U.S. Certified Co