(3022, 1, '2018-01-20 22:01:05', '2018-01-20 22:01:05', '[vc_row equal_height="yes" css=".vc_custom_1464263823580{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2"][mgt_header_block_wp title="Who we are" css=".vc_custom_1464263778264{margin-top: 0px !important;}"][vc_column_text]Professionalism and Commitment are welcome qualities in any Profession. These qualities become critical attributes in the Profession of Civil Construction. Be it a House or an Office, or a Factory, the Owners of the Property would have invested almost all their hard earned money, besides resorting to taking loans. In a vast majority of the cases, this means a Life Time Dream that needs to be fulfilled. In a Profession where both delay and cost escalation have almost become the Order of the day,<strong>PGB Constructions</strong>have emerged as a Welcome Exception in the Profession of Civil Constructions.\n\nWhile the Constructions makes a Building, it is the Interiors that convert the Building into a Sweet Home, or a Productive Factory. Always in close contact with the Owners,<strong>PGB Constructions</strong>provide attractive Interior Designs, after thoroughly understanding the aspirations of the Owners.<strong>PGB Constructions</strong>thoroughly understands that Interiors, be it for Commercial or Residential application, should, besides providing the much needed comfort, also represent the Taste and Values of the Occupants.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][mgt_promo_block_wp background_image_id="3024" coverimage="1" block_width="100%" block_height="350px" darken="no-darken" animated_overlay_color="" button_url="|||" hover_effect="bounce-to-right" text_tranform="uppercase" button_show_onhover="1" unique_block_id="80547717583"][/mgt_promo_block_wp][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1463480199968{background-color: #f8f8f8 !important;}"][vc_column][mgt_header_block_wp title="OUR BIG COMMUNITY"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width